txt.en: You have dealt a mighty blow to all foes in Talath Úrui.
Defeated foes at Magh Nûl and Magh Groth.
A scouting report is pinned to the board:\n\n'Groups of Ghâsh-hai have been spotted securing structures near Nargroth, in Talath Úrui. A brave adventurer is needed to defeat these foes.'
Ghâsh-hai can be found at Magh Nûl and Magh Groth.\n\nYou should defeat foes at these locations.
Groups of Ghâsh-hai have been spotted securing structures near Nargroth, in Talath Úrui.
